#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.71"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.71:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.71:0.2"
msgid "8. Ānandavagga "
msgstr "8. Ānanda "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.71:0.3"
msgid "71. Channasutta "
msgstr "71. With Channa "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.216, sc1
msgctxt "an3.71:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

msgctxt "an3.71:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho channo paribbājako yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā ānandena saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then the wanderer Channa went up to Venerable Ānanda and exchanged greetings with him. "

msgctxt "an3.71:1.3"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho channo paribbājako āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one side and said to Ānanda: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.71:1.4"
msgid "“tumhepi, āvuso ānanda, rāgassa pahānaṃ paññāpetha, dosassa pahānaṃ paññāpetha, mohassa pahānaṃ paññāpethā”ti. "
msgstr "“Reverend Ānanda, do you advocate giving up greed, hate, and delusion?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.71:1.5"
msgid "“Mayaṃ kho, āvuso, rāgassa pahānaṃ paññāpema, dosassa pahānaṃ paññāpema, mohassa pahānaṃ paññapemā”ti. "
msgstr "“We do, reverend.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.71:2.1"
msgid "“Kiṃ pana tumhe, āvuso, rāge ādīnavaṃ disvā rāgassa pahānaṃ paññāpetha, kiṃ dose ādīnavaṃ disvā dosassa pahānaṃ paññāpetha, kiṃ mohe ādīnavaṃ disvā mohassa pahānaṃ paññāpethā”ti? "
msgstr "“But what drawbacks have you seen, Reverend Ānanda, that you advocate giving up greed, hate, and delusion?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an3.71:3.1"
msgid "“Ratto kho, āvuso, rāgena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto attabyābādhāyapi ceteti, parabyābādhāyapi ceteti, ubhayabyābādhāyapi ceteti, cetasikampi dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti; "
msgstr "“A greedy person, overcome by greed, intends to hurt themselves, hurt others, and hurt both. They experience mental pain and sadness. "

msgctxt "an3.71:3.2"
msgid "rāge pahīne nevattabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na parabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na ubhayabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na cetasikaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
msgstr "When greed has been given up, they don’t intend to hurt themselves, hurt others, and hurt both. They don’t experience mental pain and sadness. "

msgctxt "an3.71:3.3"
msgid "Ratto kho, āvuso, rāgena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto kāyena duccaritaṃ carati, vācāya duccaritaṃ carati, manasā duccaritaṃ carati; "
msgstr "A greedy person does bad things by way of body, speech, and mind. "

msgctxt "an3.71:3.4"
msgid "rāge pahīne neva kāyena duccaritaṃ carati, na vācāya duccaritaṃ carati, na manasā duccaritaṃ carati. "
msgstr "When greed has been given up, they don’t do bad things by way of body, speech, and mind. "

msgctxt "an3.71:3.5"
msgid "Ratto kho, āvuso, rāgena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto attatthampi yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti, paratthampi yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti, ubhayatthampi yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; "
msgstr "A greedy person doesn’t truly understand what’s for their own good, the good of another, or the good of both. "

msgctxt "an3.71:3.6"
msgid "rāge pahīne attatthampi yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, paratthampi yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ubhayatthampi yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "When greed has been given up, they truly understand what’s for their own good, the good of another, or the good of both. "

msgctxt "an3.71:3.7"
msgid "Rāgo kho, āvuso, andhakaraṇo acakkhukaraṇo aññāṇakaraṇo paññānirodhiko vighātapakkhiko anibbānasaṃvattaniko. "
msgstr "Greed is a destroyer of sight, vision, and knowledge. It blocks wisdom, it’s on the side of anguish, and it doesn’t lead to extinguishment. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.217, sc4
msgctxt "an3.71:4.1"
msgid "Duṭṭho kho, āvuso, dosena … pe … "
msgstr "A hateful person, overcome by hate, intends to hurt themselves, hurt others, and hurt both. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.71:4.2"
msgid "mūḷho kho, āvuso, mohena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto attabyābādhāyapi ceteti, parabyābādhāyapi ceteti, ubhayabyābādhāyapi ceteti, cetasikampi dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti; "
msgstr "A deluded person, overcome by delusion, intends to hurt themselves, hurt others, and hurt both. They experience mental pain and sadness. "

msgctxt "an3.71:4.3"
msgid "mohe pahīne nevattabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na parabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na ubhayabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na cetasikaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
msgstr "When delusion has been given up, they don’t intend to hurt themselves, hurt others, and hurt both. They don’t experience mental pain and sadness. "

msgctxt "an3.71:4.4"
msgid "Mūḷho kho, āvuso, mohena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto kāyena duccaritaṃ carati, vācāya duccaritaṃ carati, manasā duccaritaṃ carati; "
msgstr "A deluded person does bad things by way of body, speech, and mind. "

msgctxt "an3.71:4.5"
msgid "mohe pahīne neva kāyena duccaritaṃ carati, na vācāya duccaritaṃ carati, na manasā duccaritaṃ carati. "
msgstr "When delusion has been given up, they don’t do bad things by way of body, speech, and mind. "

msgctxt "an3.71:4.6"
msgid "Mūḷho kho, āvuso, mohena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto attatthampi yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti, paratthampi yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti, ubhayatthampi yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; "
msgstr "A deluded person doesn’t truly understand what’s for their own good, the good of another, or the good of both. "

msgctxt "an3.71:4.7"
msgid "mohe pahīne attatthampi yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, paratthampi yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ubhayatthampi yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "When delusion has been given up, they truly understand what’s for their own good, the good of another, or the good of both. "

msgctxt "an3.71:4.8"
msgid "Moho kho, āvuso, andhakaraṇo acakkhukaraṇo aññāṇakaraṇo paññānirodhiko vighātapakkhiko anibbānasaṃvattaniko. "
msgstr "Delusion is a destroyer of sight, vision, and knowledge; it blocks wisdom, it’s on the side of anguish, and it doesn’t lead to extinguishment. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.71:4.9"
msgid "Idaṃ kho mayaṃ, āvuso, rāge ādīnavaṃ disvā rāgassa pahānaṃ paññāpema. "
msgstr "This is the drawback we’ve seen in greed, hate, and delusion, and this is why we advocate giving them up.” "

msgctxt "an3.71:4.10"
msgid "Idaṃ dose ādīnavaṃ disvā dosassa pahānaṃ paññāpema. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an3.71:4.11"
msgid "Idaṃ mohe ādīnavaṃ disvā mohassa pahānaṃ paññāpemā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an3.71:5.1"
msgid "“Atthi panāvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā etassa rāgassa dosassa mohassa pahānāyā”ti? "
msgstr "“But, reverend, is there a path and a practice for giving up that greed, hate, and delusion?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.71:5.2"
msgid "“Atthāvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā etassa rāgassa dosassa mohassa pahānāyā”ti. "
msgstr "“There is, reverend, a path and a practice for giving up that greed, hate, and delusion.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.71:5.3"
msgid "“Katamo panāvuso, maggo katamā paṭipadā etassa rāgassa dosassa mohassa pahānāyā”ti? "
msgstr "“Well, what is it?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.71:5.4"
msgid "“Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "“It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is: "

msgctxt "an3.71:5.5"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr "right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "

msgctxt "an3.71:5.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, maggo ayaṃ paṭipadā etassa rāgassa dosassa mohassa pahānāyā”ti. "
msgstr "This is the path, this is the practice for giving up that greed, hate, and delusion.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.71:5.7"
msgid "“Bhaddako kho, āvuso, maggo bhaddikā paṭipadā etassa rāgassa dosassa mohassa pahānāya. "
msgstr "“This is a fine path, a fine practice, for giving up that greed, hate, and delusion. "

msgctxt "an3.71:5.8"
msgid "Alañca panāvuso ānanda, appamādāyā”ti. "
msgstr "Just this much is enough to be diligent.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.71:5.9"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

